## рџЊђ Deployment

The app is available at:

- **Admin access**: [https://vacancy-project.onrender.com/](https://vacancy-project.onrender.com/)
  *(requires an administrator account)*
- **Guest access**: [https://vacancy-project.onrender.com/demo/](https://vacancy-project.onrender.com/demo/)
  *(automatic login as a guest user)*
